      "description": "## What's Changed\r\n* add parsing + safety checks around loading data from data.json by @zakhij in https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/pull/4\r\n* 6 refactor datamanager remove data state by @zakhij in https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/pull/10\r\n* 5 properly capture file activity while plugin is inactive by @zakhij in https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/pull/11\r\n* 7 accommodate upversioning by @zakhij in https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/pull/13\r\n* Revert \"7 accommodate upversioning\" by @zakhij in https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/pull/14\r\n* revert to 1.0.4 by @zakhij in https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/pull/15\r\n* 1.0.5 re-launch by @zakhij in https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/pull/16\r\n\r\nA ton of changes for data handling on the backend to improve accuracy, resilience, and evolvability, including a new schema, storing data in a new file location, and adding new metadata to file data storage (mtime) and date functions to more accurately track activity\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/zakhij/obsidian-activity-heatmap/compare/1.0.4...1.0.5",
